---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About AllTech"
  description="AllTech is a Hyde Park, UT-based IT and cybersecurity firm serving Cache Valley, the Wasatch Front, and southern Idaho since 2009."
>
  <section class="surface-dark bg-motif relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="glow-amber" style="top: -200px; right: -100px;"></div>
    <div class="relative container-wide py-20">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-4">About</div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-semibold leading-tight max-w-3xl">
        Built for the businesses<br/>that <span style="color: var(--color-amber-300);">build Cache Valley</span>.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="surface-dark py-20" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-line-faint);">
    <div class="container-prose space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
      <p>
        AllTech was founded in 2009 to meet the technical needs of Utah businesses.
        We've spent thousands of hours perfecting the relationship between
        technology and business processes — and with the way security and
        infrastructure are changing, that work has never mattered more.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today we run real infrastructure for manufacturing operations, schools,
        title companies, and multi-site SMBs. We bring enterprise tooling —
        Cloudflare Zero Trust, Darktrace, Datto RMM, Ubiquiti UniFi — down to
        where mid-market businesses can actually use it.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're not the cheapest. We're the team you call when you need it to
        actually work.
      </p>

      <div class="hairline my-10"></div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 not-prose">
        <div>
          <div class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-amber-300);">2009</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-subtle mt-1">Founded in Cache Valley</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-amber-300);">Cloudflare</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-subtle mt-1">Official Partner</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-amber-300);">In-house</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-subtle mt-1">No outsourced help desk</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
